# ERROR TIPS

### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items
### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place a entity to a tile before attempting placing
### Errors when crafting
- Ensure you have the required ingredients to craft an item
- Ensure you are crafting at a crafting machine or furnace, if the recipe requires it
### Errors when inserting
- Ensure that you have the item to insert in your inventory
- Ensure that the target entity has space for the item to be inserted
